CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778508672
OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FThis is Mr Swinney's first election
OL,7,Fvictory in five attempts over two
OL,8,Fspells as SNP leader and although he
OL,9,Ffell pretty well short of his stated
OL,10,Faim of a majority, it is a remarkable
OL,11,Fturnaround in fortunes for his party.
OL,13,FSo how exactly did Mr Swinney pull
OL,14,Fthis off?
OL,16,FAnd why did Labour fail, Reform make
OL,17,Ftheir breakthrough, the Tories hold
OL,18,Ftheir "blue wall" in the south despite
OL,19,Fcollapsing to fifth place overall, and
OL,20,Fthe Greens and Lib Dems significantly
OL,21,Fimprove their results?
OL,26,@zD@GOUzD@QO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778508672
OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FBased on conversations throughout the
OL,7,Fcampaign with more than 30 people at
OL,8,Fall levels of every main party, the
OL,9,Fmajority of which have been granted
OL,10,Fanonymity to speak freely, this is the
OL,11,Finside story of the 2026 Holyrood
OL,12,Felection.
OL,14,FThe big moment that in many ways
OL,15,Fsummed up this campaign arrived,
OL,16,Fpublicly at least, exactly one week
OL,17,Fbefore voters went to the polls.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778508672
OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FPresident Trump took to social media
OL,7,Fto announce the removal of all tariffs
OL,8,Fand restrictions on whisky imports
OL,9,Ffollowing King Charles's state visit
OL,10,Fto the US.
OL,12,FThe SNP pushed the boundaries of
OL,13,Fcredibility with a social media
OL,14,Fgraphic saying Mr Swinney "fought for
OL,15,FScotch whisky. He delivered".
OL,17,FIt was deliberate bait for opponents
OL,18,Fwho ran straight into the trap.
OL,26,@vD@[OUwD@\O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778508672
OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FThe first minister, who had made the
OL,7,Fcase for tariffs being dropped
OL,8,Fdirectly to the US President on
OL,9,Fmultiple occasions, including in the
OL,10,FOval Office, had been informed an
OL,11,Fannouncement was coming about 24 hours
OL,12,Fbefore it became public.
OL,14,FHe also received a note of thanks
OL,15,Fdirectly from President Trump and was
OL,16,F"90% sure" he would also get a phone
OL,17,Fcall from Washington.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778508672
OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FHis closest aides ` who he urged to
OL,7,Fsit down before telling them the news
OL,8,Fover the phone ` made the graphics and
OL,9,Fthen watched as Labour politicians and
OL,10,Fstaff members exploded.
OL,12,FIt's easy to see why.
OL,14,FUK government negotiators did the
OL,15,Fbehind the scenes hard yards on the
OL,16,Fdeal.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778508672
OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FAnd in the face of intense criticism
OL,7,Fit was Prime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,8,Fwho ensured the royal visit went ahead
OL,9,Fonly to once again fail to gather any
OL,10,Fcredit for a big decision.
OL,12,FBut their anger and AI-generated memes
OL,13,Fmocking Mr Swinney for claiming credit
OL,14,Ffor various major events kept the
OL,15,Fconversation on nationalist territory.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
