OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FThe candidate madness Nigel Farage had
OL,7,Fpromised to stamp out of his newly
OL,8,Fprofessionalised party was exactly
OL,9,Fwhat dominated the start of Reform
OL,10,FUK's campaign.
OL,12,FSeven failed to make it to the cut off
OL,13,Fdate for registering to stand for
OL,14,Felection with four quitting, two just
OL,15,Fdisappearing from lists and one being
OL,16,Fsuspended.
OL,18,FAn eighth quit the party just four
OL,19,Fdays before the vote.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G22/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
