FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35523
SC,0023
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778508672
OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FAnd the controversy around one who
OL,7,Fremained, Senga Beresford in Galloway
OL,8,Fand West Dumfries ran through the
OL,9,Fentire contest.
OL,11,FSome people made their hatred towards
OL,12,FReform known in a disgusting fashion.
OL,14,FStaff at the party's headquarters have
OL,15,Fto wear rubber gloves when opening
OL,16,Fpackages because "every type of
OL,17,Fexcrement" has been discovered in
OL,18,Fpostal deliveries.
OL,26,@xD@ROUyD@JO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G23/57
