OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FSeparately, high-profile candidate
OL,7,FThomas Kerr was allegedly assaulted
OL,8,Fwhile campaigning in Glasgow.
OL,10,FBut they also received good news,
OL,11,Fusually through electronic
OL,12,Fcommunication.
OL,14,FWhile I was speaking with one senior
OL,15,Ffigure, they looked at a text message
OL,16,Ffrom someone pledging #1,500 to help
OL,17,Ftheir campaign.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G24/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
