OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FThis is partially why the party
OL,7,Fremained confident of making a
OL,8,Fsignificant breakthrough, particularly
OL,9,Fin the southwest of Scotland.
OL,11,FThey regularly spoke of the potential
OL,12,Ffor a breakthrough in Ms Beresford's
OL,13,Fconstituency, where they had not long
OL,14,Fago performed well in a council
OL,15,Fbyelection, although in the end that
OL,16,Fwas never close to materialising.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G25/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
