OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778508672
OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FBut with a meeting of the Scottish
OL,7,FExecutive Committee taking place on
OL,8,FSaturday and some predicting a
OL,9,Fchallenge to his position,
OL,10,Frecriminations quickly started inside
OL,11,Fhis party.
OL,13,FOne persistent critic of Mr Sarwar
OL,14,Fsaid: "They killed off the last
OL,15,Fleader. Cleared the team. Chose the
OL,16,Fcandidates. Picked the mental
OL,17,Fstrategy. Made it all about 'Anas for
OL,18,FFM'. How can he think he can stay on?"
OL,20,FConservatives
OL,26,@vD@GOUzD@fO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G41/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35542
SC,0042
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778508672
OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FThis was always a damage limitation
OL,7,Felection for the Tories and they never
OL,8,Fhid that fact.
OL,10,FYet by polling day there was a weary
OL,11,Facceptance that the result would be at
OL,12,Fthe lower end of polling projections.
OL,14,FThe blue belt heartland along the
OL,15,FScotland/England border was a concern
OL,16,Fwith veteran campaigners privately
OL,17,Fworrying that people who live in the
OL,18,Fsouth of Scotland but travel to work
OL,19,Fin England were being swayed towards
OL,20,FReform.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G42/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35543
SC,0043
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778508672
OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FThat proved to be a false worry with
OL,7,Fhighly focused, targeted and motivated
OL,8,Fcampaigns taking place in those key
OL,9,Fconstituencies.
OL,11,FOne of the reasons for the anxiety is
OL,12,Fthat Carlisle is seen as a growing
OL,13,Fpower base for Nigel Farage's party.
OL,15,FSenior Conservatives were worrying
OL,16,Fthat water cooler chat would lead to
OL,17,Fpotential tactical voters forgetting
OL,18,F"there's a different dynamic in
OL,19,FScotland to get rid of the SNP".
OL,26,@zD@AOU{D@_O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G43/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35544
SC,0044
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778508672
OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FThe one thing that was consistent
OL,7,Famongst most Tories in their
OL,8,Fheartlands was a belief that the
OL,9,Fparty's core vote was staying true.
OL,11,FBut what they did not know was what
OL,12,Fshy tactical unionist voters were
OL,13,Fplanning to do.
OL,15,FInterestingly, Scottish leader Russell
OL,16,FFindlay had only visited the south of
OL,17,FScotland once before the home straight
OL,18,Fof campaigning, albeit one trip with
OL,19,FKemi Badenoch was cancelled when the
OL,20,FUK party leader's plans changed.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G44/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35545
SC,0045
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778508672
OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FBut when Mr Findlay did arrive he
OL,7,Fspent two days travelling west to east.
OL,9,FHe brashly ` and correctly ` said he
OL,10,Fwould protect the "blue wall" despite
OL,11,Fthe party's internal confidence waning
OL,12,Fas its collective eye moved from east
OL,13,Fto west on the electoral map.
OL,15,FFour days before voting, one well-
OL,16,Fversed doorknocker said of
OL,17,FDumfriesshire: "It's going to be very
OL,18,Ftight and definitely a scunnered
OL,19,Ffactor there.
OL,26,@yD@POU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G45/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35546
SC,0046
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778508672
OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,F"But our support is solid and
OL,7,Fmotivated. Reform a factor in both
OL,8,Fseats too, more so Finlay's (Galloway
OL,9,Fand West Dumfries)."
OL,11,FThe unrealised fear was that a Reform
OL,12,Fsurge would allow "the nats to come
OL,13,Fthrough the middle".
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@]pmqD@RpnqD@TO]tD@SOUuD@SO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G46/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35547
SC,0047
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778508672
OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FOthers tried to keep a sunny
OL,7,Fdisposition, saying the SNP vote was
OL,8,F"very soft" with anecdotal evidence
OL,9,Fof, amazingly, discontented
OL,10,Fnationalists going Tory while Reform
OL,11,Fsympathisers were persuaded to back a
OL,12,Fdarker shade of blue to give John
OL,13,FSwinney a bloody nose.
OL,15,FBut nationally as people headed to the
OL,16,Fpolls, the mood in the party's
OL,17,Fheadquarters was grim.
OL,19,FThey knew a difficult night was coming
OL,20,Fdespite believing they had run a good
OL,21,Fcampaign.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@KO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G47/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35548
SC,0048
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778508672
OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FIn 2021, the Tories almost changed
OL,7,Ftheir official logo with the electoral
OL,8,Fcommission to "Peach Party Vote
OL,9,FScottish Conservatives" to hoover up
OL,10,Fsupport on the regional list ballot.
OL,12,FThat was vetoed by then leader Douglas
OL,13,FRoss but even with similar enthusiasm
OL,14,Ffor that so-called "second vote" this
OL,15,Ftime round, they lost more than half
OL,16,Fof their MSPs.
OL,18,FDespite the glimmer of positivity in
OL,19,Fthe south, it's still looking like a
OL,20,Flong way back for the Scottish Tories.
OL,26,@pD@OOUqD@WO]vD@TOUvD@`O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G48/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35549
SC,0049
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778508672
OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FThe Scottish Greens campaign was also
OL,7,Ffocused on the peach ballot.
OL,9,FJust six candidates stood in
OL,10,Fconstituencies but the party had a
OL,11,Ftactical push for the more
OL,12,Fproportionate regional votes.
OL,14,FThis led to the party coming in for
OL,15,Fcriticism for "helping the SNP" but it
OL,16,Falso saw them secure their first ever
OL,17,Ffirst past the post victories in
OL,18,FEdinburgh Central and Glasgow
OL,19,FSouthside.
OL,26,@wD@OOUwD@_O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G49/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35550
SC,0050
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778508672
OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FIt is true though that rather than
OL,7,Fseeking out anti-SNP voters, like the
OL,8,Frest of the opposition parties, they
OL,9,Ffocused on people who were fearful of
OL,10,FReform winning seats.
OL,12,FIt also led to gains on the regional
OL,13,Flist.
OL,15,FThe Greens had a sliding scale that
OL,16,Findicated how strong a backer was from
OL,17,FG1, those seen as cast-iron supporters
OL,18,Fwho would definitely back them, to G4,
OL,19,Fwho hadn't been rude but were more
OL,20,Flikely to cast their ballot for
OL,21,Fsomeone else.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G50/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35551
SC,0051
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778508672
OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FThey ended the campaign targeting so-
OL,7,Fcalled G2s, essentially floating
OL,8,Fvoters with Green sympathies.
OL,10,FThey said that particular success
OL,11,Fcame, unsurprisingly, from SNP
OL,12,Fconstituency voters and that they
OL,13,Fpicked up people "unpromoted" offering
OL,14,Fbacking to try and keep Reform out of
OL,15,Fparliament.
OL,17,FIn 2021 the party was desperately
OL,18,Fdisappointed not to win a South
OL,19,FScotland list seat, missing out by
OL,20,Fjust 115 votes.
OL,26,@uD@ROUuD@]O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G51/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35552
SC,0052
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778508672
OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FOne canvassing session in Dumfries saw
OL,7,Ftwo-thirds of their target market say
OL,8,Fthey would vote Green.
OL,10,FTheir success was a significant factor
OL,11,Fin denying the SNP a majority but this
OL,12,Fnew Green wave should hold significant
OL,13,Fsway in the new parliament.
OL,15,FLiberal Democrats
OL,17,FThe Lib Dems were always looking north
OL,18,Fand had the resources to do it.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G52/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35553
SC,0053
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778508672
OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FScottish leader Alex Cole-Hamilton had
OL,7,Fraised #500,000 for the party since
OL,8,Fthe start of the year and was said to
OL,9,Fbelieve by the middle of the campaign
OL,10,Fthat they were on track to win nine of
OL,11,Ftheir 10 target constituencies with
OL,12,FArgyll and Bute "in the balance".
OL,14,FOthers were more conservative but
OL,15,Fmaintained supreme confidence of
OL,16,Fsignificant gains.
OL,26,@tD@QOUtD@`O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G53/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35554
SC,0054
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778508672
OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,F"The SNP bumped up a little in our
OL,7,Fdata just before/at the start of the
OL,8,Fcampaign but seem to have dropped back
OL,9,Fagain," said a source midway through
OL,10,Fthe push for votes.
OL,12,FNone of the team saw the seismic shift
OL,13,Fcoming that saw the party lose its
OL,14,Fheartland of Shetland, a constituency
OL,15,Fit had held since the first Holyrood
OL,16,Felection in 1999.
OL,18,FBut while the most optimistic
OL,19,Fpredictions did not quite pan out,
OL,20,Fthey did pick up seven of those 10
OL,21,Ftargets.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@GO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G54/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35555
SC,0055
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778508672
OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FOne significant change in Liberal
OL,7,Fcampaigning was a shift to focus on
OL,8,Fthat peach vote as well as a small
OL,9,Fnumber of first past the post contests.
OL,11,FIndeed, Mr Cole-Hamilton carried out a
OL,12,Fseries of eye-catching peach-themed
OL,13,Fstunts including wearing a garish suit
OL,14,Fas polling day approached.
OL,16,FMuch of this was driven by the
OL,17,Fdefection of Jamie Greene from the
OL,18,FConservatives, who was able to give
OL,19,Fthe party a debrief on the successful
OL,20,FTory campaign five years ago.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G55/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35556
SC,0056
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778508672
OL,3,CInside the metaphors and mess of the
OL,4,CHolyrood election campaign
OL,6,FBut a breakthrough was also made in
OL,7,Ffocus groups. When the party asked
OL,8,Fpeople why they didn't back them on
OL,9,Fthe regional ballot, the answer was
OL,10,Fsimple: "Because you don't ask us to."
OL,12,FThis led to them being confident of
OL,13,Fgaining a South Scotland list seat.
OL,15,FAs Duncan Dunlop was confirmed as an
OL,16,FMSP late in the day, the noise in the
OL,17,Fparty's headquarters was such that one
OL,18,Fofficial got a warning on their
OL,19,Fsmartwatch about the "loud
OL,20,Fenvironment" reaching 90 decibels.
OL,26,@rD@IOUrD@fO]{D@VOU|D@LO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G56/57
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
